responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "241E08FD47CB14F2B4EA4C8BBFE46FEF", "Can\'t say, Captain. But that metal is a stronger clue. It\'s Bloomsteel, a strong metal forged only for Aelan royals and their guard. If you can\'t find the chest, the key might be more valuable. Ha!")
